@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@accessToken = paste-access-token-here
@roomId = paste-project-room-id-here
@voiceRoomId = paste-voice-room-id-here

### 보이스챗 방 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/voice/rooms
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": "{{roomId}}"
}

### 보이스챗 방 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/voice/rooms/{{voiceRoomId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### LiveKit 접속 토큰 발급
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/voice/rooms/{{voiceRoomId}}/token
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 마이크 상태 변경
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/voice/rooms/{{voiceRoomId}}/mic
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "micStatus": "MUTED"
}

### 통화 나가기
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/voice/rooms/{{voiceRoomId}}/leave
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 통화 종료 (생성자만)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/voice/rooms/{{voiceRoomId}}/end
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
